        complexity: { time: 'O(4^n * n)', space: 'O(n)' },
        approach: 'Classic backtracking. At depth i, iterate every letter the i-th digit maps to, push it, recurse, pop. The recursion tree has up to 4^n leaves (digits 7 and 9 have four letters); each leaf does O(n) work to build the string.',
