        approach: "Dutch National Flag. Three pointers carve the array into [0s | 1s | unknown | 2s]. On a 0 swap with lo and advance both; on a 1 just advance mid; on a 2 swap with hi and shrink hi WITHOUT advancing mid (the swapped-in value is unexamined). The function also returns nums so the driver can read the in-place result.",
